  "title": "chore(deps): update dependency rollup-plugin-babel to v4.3.2",
  "body": "This PR contains the following updates:\n\n| Package | Type | Update | Change | References |\n|---|---|---|---|---|\n| rollup-plugin-babel | devDependencies | patch | `4.3.0` -> `4.3.2` | [source](https://togithub.com/rollup/rollup-plugin-babel) |\n\n---\n\n### Release Notes\n\n<details>\n<summary>rollup/rollup-plugin-babel</summary>\n\n### [`v4.3.2`](https://togithub.com/rollup/rollup-plugin-babel/blob/master/CHANGELOG.md#&#8203;432)\n\n[Compare Source](https://togithub.com/rollup/rollup-plugin-babel/compare/v4.3.1...v4.3.2)\n\n-   Fixed usage with `externalHelpers: true` option\n\n### [`v4.3.1`](https://togithub.com/rollup/rollup-plugin-babel/blob/master/CHANGELOG.md#&#8203;431)\n\n[Compare Source](https://togithub.com/rollup/rollup-plugin-babel/compare/v4.3.0...v4.3.1)\n\n-   Add `.js` extension to the virtual babel helpers file (only matters when using `preserveModules` option in rollup)\n\n</details>\n\n---\n\n### Renovate configuration\n\n:date: **Schedule**: \"every weekend\" in timezone Europe/Paris.\n\n:vertical_traffic_light: **Automerge**: Enabled.\n\n:recycle: **Rebasing**: Whenever PR is stale, or if you modify the PR title to begin with \"`rebase!`\".\n\n:no_bell: **Ignore**: Close this PR and you won't be reminded about this update again.\n\n---\n\n - [ ] <!-- renovate-rebase -->If you want to rebase/retry this PR, check this box\n\n---\n\nThis PR has been generated by [Renovate Bot](https://togithub.com/marketplace/renovate). View repository job log [here](https://renovatebot.com/dashboard#algolia/instantsearch.js).",
